Install instructions
====================

1. Create new MySQL database.

2. Create database structure by running schema.sql

3. Write you database connection settings to conf.php

4. Move the contents of the archive to your webserver.
   (INSTALL and schema.sql are not needed there).

5. Point your browser to the install location.
   Have fun!


Notes
=====

Requires JavaScript and CSS to work correctly.


Tested on:

* MS Internet Explorer 6 and 7
* Mozilla Firefox 2.0.0.1
* Opera 9.20
* Konqueror 3.5.5


